	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "parse outcomes now emit consistent telemetry and user-facing diagnostics from shared command-boundary helpers." ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "wire parse boundary into observability pipeline" ;
